item.title: CVE-2023-5777|2024-08-02T08:07:32.769Z -- weintek -- easybuilder%20pro
item.description: Weintek EasyBuilder Pro contains a vulnerability that, even when the private key is immediately deleted after the crash report transmission is finished, the private key is exposed to the public, which could result in obtaining remote control of the crash report server.
